data.description: Most affordable cute and cozy 3 bedroom, 2 bath POOL home in PSJ nestled on a CORNER LOT with a large screen enclosed patio, privacy fenced yard with double gate to backyard, charming waterfall feature, grilling deck and a storage shed boasting access doors from the front yard and back yard. Ideas for outdoor living and entertaining are limited only to your imagination with NO DEED RESTRICTIONS. Home has SKYLIGHTS for abundant natural light and great outside views and ceiling fans in each room. LOW MAINTENANCE here as major systems have been updated to include 2022 water heater, 2021 HVAC and 2017 roof! Relax in this quaint neighborhood that is close to shopping, entertainment and restaurants, schools, parks, churches, banks and medical offices.
